Added Last.fm integration: Last.fm is a service that can automatically track what music you are listening to e.g. by connecting it to your Spotify account. After you enabled the integration which can be done in the app settings Diarium will show you on each entry what music you listened to on that day incl. your top artists or tracks When long pressing the location on a journal entry Diarium will show a context menu allowing you to open the location in Google Maps or to remove the location Templates are now sorted alphabetically Many more smaller changes improvements Happy journaling!
